race.description: On The Clock To Book Trials
race.comment: ZIPPING URBAN (4) has proven too strong with wins at his last two, scoring by 5 lengths (25.35) last time and by 5.5 lengths (30.13) two back. Got the money at his only try from this box. Looks to have an edge on most of these. FLYAWAY JACK (1) failed to come into contention last start after drifting back at Q Lakeside, but prior to that won by half a length at Q Straight (16.40) beating Kickin' Tyres in a Grade 5 on October 20. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings three times from three starts. Can do much better this time. MILLIE BEACH (3) turned in a plain effort last time when fifth at this track over 366m behind Zipping Choi (20.39) in a Grade 5. Shapes as one to consider. HARA'S MILLY (2) will give backers a sight.
